### 파이프라인 시작 (202 Accepted)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/1/pipeline/start
Accept: application/json

### 파이프라인 최신 상태 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/1/pipeline
Accept: application/json

### 파이프라인 실행 이력 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/1/pipeline/history
Accept: application/json

### SSE 스트림 연결 (브라우저 또는 curl로 테스트)
# curl -N http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/1/pipeline/events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/1/pipeline/events
Accept: text/event-stream
